high_descs: Turn around, go straight and slightly to the left to face the cabinet above the toaster.
Open the cabinet and remove the black plate inside.
Move to the left and face the microwave.
Place the dish inside of the microwave, turn it on, and remove the dish.
Turn to the right to face the counter next to the toaster.
Place the dish on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Place the microwaved dish on top of the counter next to the toaster.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the cupboard above the toaster.
Open the cupboard door, remove the black plate, close the cupboard door.
Turn to your left and stand in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the plate on the left side of the turntable, close the door, turn the microwave on; after the microwave turns off, open the door, pick up the plate, close the door.
Turn to your right to the counter with the toaster on it.
Place the plate on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Get a plate from the cupboard, place the plate to the left of the toaster

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge, turn right and walk over to the counter then look up.
Open the cabinet door above the toaster and take out the grey plate, then close the cabinet.
Look down and turn left to face the microwave.
Microwave the grey plate for a couple seconds in the microwave to heat it up, then take it out.
Turn right to face the counter.
Put the heated grey plate on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated grey plate on the counter.
